<emphasis bold="true" box="[199,315,1081,1106]" pageId="6" pageNumber="139">Remarks.</emphasis>
This species was described in detail by 
<bibRefCitation box="[786,1087,1081,1106]" pageId="6" pageNumber="139" refString="Viraktamath, C. A., Dai, W. &amp; Zhang, Y. L. (2012) Taxonomic revision of the leafhopper tribe Agalliini (Hemiptera: Cicadellidae: Megophthalminae) from China, with description of new taxa. Zootaxa, 3430, 1 - 49." type="journal article">
